nodes.text: Domm  was a male Zabrak criminal living inside the Greenwood Station dome on Nox. In 25,793 BBY he was visited by Tre Sana and the Je'daii Ranger Lanoree Brock, who pressed him for information regarding the location of Maxhagan. Lanoree Brock used the Force to erase Domm's memory after the encounter so that he would not report on them.
